title: Ken Livingstone on Hitler and Zionism - Historian Lenni Brenner
description: Ken Livingstone on Hitler and Zionism - Historian Lenni Brenner is Interviewed.mp4 - 40min 55s 640 x 480 Amid charges that former London Mayor Ken Livingstone was anti-Semitic in what he said about Zionist organizations in the 1930's, Lenni Brenner who wrote "Zionism in the Age of the Dictators" explains there was for years real collaboration between major Zionist organizations and the Nazi government. The powerful Jewish led anti-Nazi boycott was effectively sabotaged by the Zionists.
